OVERVIEW

  'DIRTY' is a minimal toolkit for making games / interactive experiences.
  https://dirty.enemyspy.xyz/

BUILD

  $ make lib

  will create `libdirty.a` under `build/lib/`

  $ make examples

  will build all examples under `examples` to `build/bin/`


USAGE

  // create window
  void d_init(const char* title, int width, int height)

  // run main loop
  void d_run(void (*f)(void))

